# Eleventy input exclusions. Input is the repo root (dir.input: '.') and we run with
# setUseGitIgnore(false), so everything that is NOT site content must be listed here.
# Eleventy only processes templateFormats (md, njk); node_modules is always ignored.
# Built/vendored trees
_site
vendor
pdf-output
# Passthrough-copied (do not template-process; addPassthroughCopy still copies them)
assets
resources
# Repo docs / meta markdown (not site pages)
README.md
CONTRIBUTE.md
CHANGELOG.md
claude.md
roadmap.md
LICENSE.txt
doc
# Tooling
scripts
tests
hooks
lib
